race.comment: TORONESS (3) was well in the betting at Toowoomba last time out and didn't let supporters down shedding the maiden tag on that occasion. Will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory and can go right on with the job now. DEL TITO (7) got the maiden out of the way over this track and trip last start before being tipped out for further time to mature. Has revved up for this with two recent trials and can run a race while fresh. WANT TO BE PROUD (4) is aided by the inside marble and is a player form there along with BACCARAT ROUGE (6) who was  fresh winner at this track and trip two back.
